# Images Repository Code Owners
# This file defines code ownership for custom image development
# Development Teams own their team-specific images
# Operations Team owns base templates and compliance requirements

# Base templates and compliance requirements - Operations Team ONLY
/packer/base/ @operations-team

# Team-specific image customizations
/packer/teams/vscode* @vscode-team-leads
/packer/teams/java* @java-team-leads
/packer/teams/dotnet* @dotnet-team-leads

# DevBox Definitions - Development Team Leads with Operations review
# Operations team should be notified of changes but dev leads can approve
/definitions/ @dev-leads @operations-team

# Build scripts - Any team lead can approve
/packer/build-image.ps1 @dev-leads

# Documentation
/README.md @dev-leads @operations-team
